00:00:31.260 --> 00:00:34.260
♫ Ne razumem sebe, ♫

00:00:34.260 --> 00:00:39.260
♫ zašto oni i dalje o ljubavi govore, ♫

00:00:39.260 --> 00:00:42.260
♫ ako mi priđu, ♫

00:00:42.260 --> 00:00:48.260
♫ pogledaju me u oči i poljube ruku. ♫

00:00:48.260 --> 00:00:51.260
♫ Ne razumem sebe, ♫

00:00:51.260 --> 00:00:56.260
♫ zašto o magiji govore, ♫

00:00:56.260 --> 00:00:58.260
♫ kojoj niko ne može da se odupre, ♫

00:00:58.260 --> 00:01:07.260
♫ ako me on vidi, ako prođe pored mene. ♫

00:01:07.260 --> 00:01:13.260
♫ Ali ako se upali crveno svetlo ♫

00:01:13.260 --> 00:01:16.260
♫ usred noći ♫

00:01:16.260 --> 00:01:20.260
♫ i pesmu moju slušaju svi, ♫

00:01:20.260 --> 00:01:30.260
♫ onda je jednostavno videti. ♫

00:01:30.260 --> 00:01:39.260
♫ Moje usne ljube žarko, ♫

00:01:39.260 --> 00:01:48.260
♫ moji udovi, oni su beli i savitljivi. ♫

00:01:48.260 --> 00:01:55.260
♫ Zapisano mi je u zvezdama, ♫

00:01:55.260 --> 00:02:02.260
♫ ljubićeš, volećeš. ♫

00:02:02.260 --> 00:02:08.260
♫ Moja stopala, ona klize i lebde, ♫

00:02:08.260 --> 00:02:17.260
♫ moje oči, one mame i sjaje. ♫

00:02:17.260 --> 00:02:27.260
♫ A ja plešem zaluđena jer znam, ♫

00:02:27.260 --> 00:02:39.260
♫ moje usne tako žarko ljube. ♫

00:03:16.260 --> 00:03:19.260
♫ U mojim venama ♫

00:03:19.260 --> 00:03:23.260
♫ teče krv plesačice ♫

00:03:23.260 --> 00:03:26.260
♫ jer je moja divna majka ♫

00:03:26.260 --> 00:03:29.260
♫ bila kraljica plesa ♫

00:03:29.260 --> 00:03:33.260
♫ u zlatnom Alkazaru. ♫

00:03:33.260 --> 00:03:36.260
♫ Ona je bila prekrasna, ♫

00:03:36.260 --> 00:03:41.260
♫ često sam je u snovima viđala. ♫

00:03:41.260 --> 00:03:44.260
♫ Ako je svirala daire ♫

00:03:44.260 --> 00:03:54.260
♫ u svom čarobnom plesu, 
sve oči su je sa divljenjem gledale. ♫

00:03:54.260 --> 00:03:59.260
♫ Ona se probudila u meni, ♫

00:03:59.260 --> 00:04:02.260
♫ plešem istim zanosom. ♫

00:04:02.260 --> 00:04:05.260
♫ Plešem kao ona u ponoć ♫

00:04:05.260 --> 00:04:13.260
♫ i osećam duboko u sebi: ♫

00:04:15.260 --> 00:04:24.260
♫ moje usne ljube žarko, ♫

00:04:24.260 --> 00:04:33.260
♫ moji udovi, oni su gipki i beli. ♫

00:04:33.260 --> 00:04:41.260
♫ Zapisano mi je u zvezdama, ♫

00:04:41.260 --> 00:04:49.260
♫ volećeš, ljubićeš. ♫

00:05:01.260 --> 00:05:13.260
♫ A ja plešem zaluđena jer znam ♫

00:05:13.260 --> 00:05:30.260
♫ da moje usne tako žarko ljube ♫

